reviewText: I don't actually have this DVD, but I don't understand how this disk can be described as "Chick Corea's and Gary Burton's first appearance as a duo, which took place at the Philharmonie in Munich in 1997."  I saw them perform together in the late 1970s. Crystal Silence was first released in 1973.  This sounds illegitimate.
All though it was good it fell a little short of what I was looking for from chick.  Actually I felt like he was carrying Gary.
This DVD has acquired a permanent place in my Mac laptop, what more can I say . .
